query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND (n.name like '%r%' OR n.name like '%f%' OR n.name like '%w%' OR n.name like '%p%' OR n.name like '%Z%') AND n.gender in ('m') AND it2.info in ('genres','plot','pictorial','LD audio quality','LD number of sides','adaption','LD pressing plant','rating','LD spaciality','certificates','taglines','LD dialogue intellegibility','portrayed in','nick names','LD subtitles','tech info','bottom 10 rank','locations','LD laserdisc title','height','LD color information') AND cct1.kind in ('complete+verified','complete','crew') AND (k.keyword like '%alien%' OR k.keyword like '%assassin%' OR k.keyword like '%sacrifice%') AND (chn.name like '%John Wick%' OR chn.name like '%Rocky Balboa%' OR chn.name like '%Clarice Starling%') AND (t.title like '%spoon%' OR t.title like '%house%' OR t.title like '%light%' OR t.title like '%shoe%') AND t.production_year < 2010 AND mi_idx.info > '2.0'
